column1: Add on module in woocommerce orders
column3: We will launching an ecommerce site Running using woocommerce and WCFM plugin. We needs to hire person which can create a simple datalist from woocommerce order.  Scenario All the vendors inside our ecommerce are our own people which selling product from our warehouse. All them sell the same product.  We divide the vendors into 2 membership, which level is stokist, level 2 is store  When we got orders from store/stokist, our warehouse will processing the orders and create a boxs and start to ship. In here, we needs extras module because after we finish assemble the orders, we will send to stokist outlet first. What I needs is?  1) I needs at warehouse there is a datalist system for all order had been made by customers. This purpose for warehouse use. In datatlist will show all order sort and search by stokis name, state name, order date name, or customer name). Its also not show all category product orders will except certain category products. Also its show only processing order status only by default but can search for complete enquiry.( Or you can make a settings for me to select which status and category for this datalist)  2) They will print the package slip from the customers orders and paste the slip into the parcel box of customers. Inside the slip we needs a 3 QR barcode. 1 qr barcode is when staff complete wrap the box, they scan the barcode (to make indicator inside the datalist mark as ready to ship to stokist use lorry transport). Then 2, qr barcode is for stokist outlet when receive the parcel box (this will mark as received at stokist outlet). 3, barcode for pickup person to take out from stokist outlet (mark as ship ot from stokist outlet name). We also need the bulk summary report for searcable period for commision paid to stokist regarding from the orders of customer. Easy to say, report they received quantity of product at stokist.  3) Then online store person/delivery boy will take the parcel box and ship to customer. This will use WC Lovers plugin. If we can integrate into this WC Lovers system maby a good way.   4) Another module, we needs to capture data from others ecoommerce website. They shop are selling our product also in they website. They will upload all their orders and customer name details into google sheet. We needs to capture the data, and show it into our datalist at warehouse. The procedures is same above. Staf print the package slip and paste then scan the barcode, then the stokist also scan the barcode after received. So in package slip must have different identity from our company. After the parcel arrive at stokist, they runner will take the orders and scan the barcode for leaving the stokist outlet. And we also needs details report for this module because we need create a bulk inovice to give to this website. So everyday, we can set a batch report and invoices to print out and send to this website admin.  5) And for admin purpose, we can see from the datalist the product about their locations and status. We can monitor and fix any human erros while ship and deliver the products.  Thank you.Categoría: Programación y TecnologíaSubcategoría: Wordpress¿Cuál es el alcance del proyecto?: Desarrollo de sitio personalizado¿Es un proyecto o una posición?: Un proyectoActualmente tengo: No aplicaDisponibilidad requerida: Según se necesiteIntegraciones de API: Cloud Storage (Dropbox, Google Drive, etc.)

column1: Desarrollo de website para crear collages con Drag and Drop / Drag ...
column3: I need to develop a website where users can drag and drop many images and generate a moodboard.  "A moodboard is a trend panel that consists of a collage of images, text and object samples in a composition. It can be based on a theme or be any randomly chosen material." The images will be placed in random sizes but the user may reorder and resize them as desired. There is also the possibility of pasting whatever you have on your clipboard. The composition will be sized and ordered according to the amount of images dragged.    It will have a limit of images, since it would be convenient that for a larger moodboard, they can pay for it. Attached is a quick prototype made in Figma to understand the concept: https://bit.ly/35Kag8k Project open to non-detailed functionalities and can be discussed with the programmer.  Ideal features: - Sign in with Google - Profile with saved moodboards - Moodboards that can be shared by URL Featured Moodboards - Save moodboards in png and jpg - change to black or white moodboard background - create minimum 3 color averages of all pasted images - paste things from the clipboard - payment system to unlock more functions  ///  Necesito desarrollar una website en la que se puedan arrastrar y soltar muchas imágenes y se genere un moodboard.  "Un moodboard es un panel de tendencias que consiste en un collage que consta de imágenes, texto y muestras de objetos en una composición. Pueda estar basado en un tema o tratarse de cualquier material escogido al azar." Las imágenes se colocarán en tamaños al azar pero el usuario podría reordenarlas y redimensionarlas a su gusto. También existe la posibilidad de que peguen lo que tengan en su portapapeles. La composición tendrá un tamaño y ordenamiento acorde a la cantidad de imágenes arrastradas.    Tendrá un límite de imágenes, ya que sería conveniente que para un moodboard más grande, puedan pagar para conseguirlo. Adjunto prototipo rápido hecho en Figma para entender el concepto: https://bit.ly/35Kag8k Proyecto abierto a funcionalidades no detalladas y conversables con el programador.  Funciones ideales: - Iniciar sesión con Google - Perfil con moodboards guardados - Moodboards compartibles por URL - Moodboards destacados - Poder guardar moodboards en PNG y JPG - Cambiar fondo de moodboard en blanco y en negro - Poder crear mínimo promedios de colores de todas las imágenes pegadas - Poder pegar cosas del portapapeles - Sistema de pago para desbloquear más funcionesCategoría: Programación y TecnologíaSubcategoría: Programación Web¿Cuál es el alcance del proyecto?: Crear un nuevo sitio personalizado¿Es un proyecto o una posición?: Un proyectoActualmente tengo: Tengo las especificacionesDisponibilidad requerida: Según se necesiteIntegraciones de API: Payment Processor (Paypal, Stripe, etc.)Roles necesarios: Programador

You are passionate about translating a proven user-experience journey into a smooth and intuitive interface. Ideally, you’re also experienced with charting libraries.  *Required Technical Expertise* -Expertise programming in HTML and knowledge in CSS3+ and JavaScript -Experience with frameworks such as Vue (preferably) or React -Experience with JavaScript-based charting libraries, like Chart.js -Cross-browser and mobile responsive development -Ability to work successfully in a team, and take initiatives on tasks -Good understanding of software development processes like Scrum and Agile  *Existing UI design and formatted data* The successful candidate will work off a finalised UI design and charts in Sketch, with the full navigation on Invision, as well as fully-formatted data.  *About US* We are the data analytics platform for the impact sector. It automates the analysis and visualisation of impact data and presents social and environmental performance based on any given impact measurement framework.  *Beyond this project* The candidate will have the opportunity to work with us, beyond the Vodafone Foundation project, to shape a user-centric application, based on a wealth of data, fed through automated data structures.  *Please get in touch*Categoría: Programación y TecnologíaSubcategoría: Programación Web¿Cuál es el alcance del proyecto?: Crear un nuevo sitio personalizado¿Es un proyecto o una posición?: Un proyectoActualmente tengo: Tengo las especificacionesDisponibilidad requerida: Según se necesiteIntegraciones de API: Cloud Storage (Dropbox, Google Drive, etc.)Roles necesarios: Programador, Diseñador
